{"tid":1694180,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"國產貨多左後 最近開始有啲肚痛 頭痛 暈","createTime":"2019-11-05T04:12:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-06T04:48:20.000Z","uid":198595,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8cb0ad60532ac7fa78c7ec8b58efedd7e745f436","tid":1694180,"uid":198595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T04:12:48.000Z","msg":"呢排成日小小肚痛 有時心跳快左<br />\n以前有操過 心跳慢過普通人<br />\n耐無操心率都仲慢<br />\n呢排開始慢慢操返<br />\n但呢排開始間唔中心率快左<br />\n又有時會頭痛 有啲暈 有啲痕<br />\n整體身體差左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跟住上網見到話氰化物中毒有小小似有小小輕微症狀<br />\n最近有時唔小心行街shopping吸到國產貨<br />\n懷疑會短命好多年或者突然暴斃了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有無人都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可以點做去改善下<br />\n好似不可逆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0eedb7e12520d3e6823c018e139f4c1db729cfad","tid":1694180,"uid":198595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T04:21:23.000Z","msg":"開錯台 屌"},{"pid":"d621e90f7516d2b9c7b2efbcf3c4c0c91083182a","tid":1694180,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T04:22:14.000Z","msg":"休息下 都係 搵杏林"},{"pid":"7a502a8412e53120f40d0295f4b033227d4e324e","tid":1694180,"uid":198595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d621e90f7516d2b9c7b2efbcf3c4c0c91083182a","tid":1694180,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T04:22:14.000Z","msg":"休息下 都係 搵杏林"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T04:28:40.000Z","msg":"估唔到開錯台既有人覆先 仲去返健康台開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唉唔知點 買左啲枇杷膏飲 跟住又跟單整涼茶 真係再差先試下搵啦 唔想搵住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b255f0a67a63e38093a8e650de0f87d4a926900a","tid":1694180,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7a502a8412e53120f40d0295f4b033227d4e3